  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nAllow enabling or disabling use of the builder API on a per-validator basis. We could store information about whether the builder API should be used for a validator in the validator definitions file. This would give us all the functionality described by the config file in this issue: https://github.com/flashbots/mev-boost/issues/154 event though we don't directly support that format right now.\r\n\r\nThe changes required would be very similar to those made in this PR for gas limit. I may end up just adding these changes there in order to avoid conflicts https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/pull/3342\r\n\r\n",
